        linkml:permissible_values  <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveImmersion#WaterDipping> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveImmersion#Water> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveImmersion#Other> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveImmersion#Oil> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveImmersion#Multi> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveImmersion#Glycerol> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveImmersion#Air> .

