        linkml:permissible_values  <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#VioletCorrected> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#UV> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Achro> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Achromat> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Apo> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Fl> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Fluar> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Fluor> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Fluotar> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Neofluar> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#Other> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#PlanApo> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#PlanFluor> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#PlanNeofluar> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/ObjectiveCorrection#SuperFluor> .

