Minus> <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Other> );
        linkml:permissible_values  <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#XeFl> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#XeCl> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#XeBr> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Xe> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#TiSapphire> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Ruby> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Rhodamine6G> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Other> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#NdYAG> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#NdGlass> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#N> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#KrFl> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#KrCl> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Kr> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#HoYLF> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#HoYAG> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#HeNe> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#HeCd> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#HFl> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#H2O> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#GaAs> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Ag> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Alexandrite> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Ar> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#ArCl> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#ArFl> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#CO> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#CO2> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#CoumarinC30> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#Cu> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#EMinus> , <https://ld.openmicroscopy.org/core/LaserLaserMedium#ErG